Words.40000.Tooltip: The Heavy Pistol is surprisingly powerful for a weapon of its size, but has a high recoil.

Words.40001.Tooltip: The Light Pistol is a standard-issue firearm, with high firerate and accuracy but low damage.
Words.40002.Name: Revolver
Words.40002.Tooltip: The Revolver is exceptionally powerful with a decent range, but is very slow and holds only six bullets at a time.
Words.40003.Name: Assault Rifle
Words.40003.Tooltip: The Assault Rifle is a balanced weapon overall, offering a high rate of fire with moderate stopping power.
Words.40004.Name: Machine Pistol
Words.40004.Tooltip: The Machine Pistol fires a continuous stream of bullets, but has a high recoil and poor accuracy with a low range.
Words.40005.Name: Shotgun
Words.40005.Tooltip: The Shotgun sprays 10 damaging pellets at nearby targets. It's very slow, but extremely effective at close range.
Words.40006.Name: Burstfire Pistol
Words.40006.Tooltip: The Burstfire Pistol fires quick bursts of three bullets. It is extremely light and fast, but suffers from low damage and poor accuracy.
Words.40007.Name: Bolt-Action Rifle
Words.40007.Tooltip: The Bolt-Action Rifle is an extremely long-range, extremely powerful weapon, but a new bullet must be loaded into the chamber after each shot.
Words.40008.Name: Combat Rifle
Words.40008.Tooltip: The Combat Rifle is an extremely long-range semi-automatic weapon with moderate stopping power.
Words.40009.Name: Burstfire Rifle
Words.40009.Tooltip: The Burstfire Rifle fires quick bursts of three bullets, with a tight spread.
Words.40010.Name: Submachine Gun
Words.40010.Tooltip: The SMG is an extremely fast automatic weapon, though the individual bullets don't pack much punch.
Words.40011.Name: Light Machine Gun
Words.40011.Tooltip: The Light Machine Gun has a high ammo capacity, but sacrifices accuracy for the sheer volume of bullets.
Words.40013.Name: Tactical SMG
Words.40013.Tooltip: The Tactical SMG offers an extremely high rate of fire and mobility, but with a high spread and recoil.
Words.40014.Name: LMG Recon
Words.40014.Tooltip: The lightweight machine gun reconnaissance has a quick reload speed and high damage, but very low accuracy and low rate of fire.
Words.40015.Name: Breech Loaded Pistol
Words.40015.Tooltip: The Breech Loaded Pistol that can be bored to use exotic ammunition.
Words.40016.Name: Shotgun AR-k
Words.40016.Tooltip: The Shotgun Assault Rifle-k fires 5 pellets and offers a high rate of fire but is highly inaccurate at a distance.
Words.40017.Name: Heavy Assault Rifle
Words.40017.Tooltip: The Heavy Assault Rifle may not be fast, but it makes up for it in sheer stopping power and range.
Words.40018.Name: Burstfire SMG
Words.40018.Tooltip: The Burstfire SMG fires a 4 round burst with good accuracy and low recoil, but has low damage and range.
Words.40019.Name: Anti-Materiel Rifle
Words.40019.Tooltip: The Anti-Materiel Rifle is instantly lethal at any range, but has a long reload time after every shot. No one man should have all this power!
Words.40020.Name: Bullpup Full Auto
Words.40020.Tooltip: The Bullpup Full Auto is lightweight and has strong short to mid-range stopping power, but is slow to reload and has very limited range.
Words.40021.Name: Snub 260
Words.40021.Tooltip: A compact snubnose revolver with a higher rate of fire but less punch than larger revolvers and poor range.
Words.40022.Name: M4X Rifle
Words.40022.Tooltip: The M4X Rifle is a balanced weapon overall, offering high rate of fire with moderate stopping power.
Words.40023.Name: AK470 Rifle
Words.40023.Tooltip: The AK470 Rifle is a balanced weapon overall, offering moderate rate of fire with high stopping power.
Words.40024.Name: Compound Bow

Words.40025.Name: Tactical Assault Rifle
